---
## build edge mask
```c
static inline void ntacle_build_masks()
{
    for(int n=0;n<162;n++)
    {
        NodeMask m = {0};
        int d = adjacency_count[n];
        int o = adjacency_offset[n];
        for(int k=0;k<d;k++)
        {
            int nb = adjacency_table[o+k];
            m.w[nb>>6] |= 1ULL<<(nb&63);
        }
        ntacle_edge_mask[n] = m;
    }
}
```
---
# Diffusion Step
