# Fast Version (Bit Scan)
เร็วกว่า
```c
static inline NodeMask ntacle_diffuse_fast(NodeMask m)
{
    NodeMask out = m;
    for(int w=0;w<3;w++)
    {
        uint64_t v = m.w[w];
        while(v)
        {
            int b = __builtin_ctzll(v);
            v &= v-1;
            int node = (w<<6) + b;
            NodeMask e = ntacle_edge_mask[node];
            out.w[0] |= e.w[0];
            out.w[1] |= e.w[1];
            out.w[2] |= e.w[2];
            out.w[3] |= e.w[3];
        }
    }
    return out;
}
```
cost
```
O(active nodes)
```
ถ้า active 5 node → 5 iteration
